- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper uses machine learning techniques to improve the performance of dependency parsing. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a possible category as the paper focuses on neural network-based parsers. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a less likely category, but still possible as dependency parsing is a common technique used in information retrieval tasks.
